name: #003 Lando Norris McLaren 2021
description:
Lando Norris (1999-) is a British F1 driver, who've started in F1 in 2019.

He only had 5 podiums, was pole position 1 time, but never won a championship... YET! 

Norris is a rising star. In Russian GP 2021, he battled side by side with seven-times champion Lewis Hamilton for the 1st place. He had his chance, but a heavy rain in the final laps have settled his fate, unfortunaly
 

He's on his way to achieve his 1st victory in 2021 driving McLaren car MCL35M.


Keep fighting, Norris!
